Comment.MultiLanguageText: Use this to activate the No Go Zone

AttributeList.Text: Machine Type Move Z1, Z2 Limits
If the Object is installed, do not allow the relative or absolute Z axis motion in the top part of the stroke, jogging should be still possible. Safety condition for the printing sequence.
Do not allow any Z axis motion in the top part of the stroke, if the printhead is over the Object.
Do not allow any motion when the Object is in a collision with axes.
Homing order to prevent axis collision
